Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.52,0:46:35.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只是为了检查一下你对教材的理解程度
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.88,0:46:41.78,English,,0,0,0,,I think if you read this if you read the book each chapter three times and work the practice problems
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.88,0:46:41.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为如果你阅读这本书，如果你每一章读三遍，并做练习
