Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:55.46,English,,0,0,0,,The other book we use is the Kernighan and Ritchie's classic C programming book
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:55.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们使用的另一本书是 Kernighan 和 Ritchie 的经典 C 编程书
