Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.38,0:47:30.66,English,,0,0,0,,But it's a kind of book you can just read from beginning to end
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.38,0:47:30.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这是一本书，你从头到尾读一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.18,0:47:33.82,English,,0,0,0,,And get a really good understanding of C
