Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.34,0:47:41.54,English,,0,0,0,,There's four main components to the course
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.34,0:47:41.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这门课有四个主要组成部分
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.54,0:47:46.46,English,,0,0,0,,There's lectures where we go over the high level concepts, recitations where
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.54,0:47:46.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,包括从较高层次讲解概念的讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.82,0:47:52.48,English,,0,0,0,,Which meet once a week for an hour led by a TA
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.82,0:47:52.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,时长一个小时，每周由助教主持一次的复习课，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.48,0:47:56.36,English,,0,0,0,,The purpose of the recitations is really to help you with the labs
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.48,0:47:56.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,复习课的目的是帮助你做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.82,0:47:58.70,English,,0,0,0,,So it's very practical and hands-on
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.82,0:47:58.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这是非常实用的而且是亲自动手的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.64,0:48:05.82,English,,0,0,0,,There's seven of those labs and these are really the heart and soul of the course
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.64,0:48:05.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些实验有七个，这些都是课程的核心和灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.82,0:48:09.26,English,,0,0,0,,This is where all the real learning comes in I think
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.82,0:48:09.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为这就是真正的学习的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.26,0:48:11.87,English,,0,0,0,,When you actually have to do this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.26,0:48:11.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你亲自去做这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.46,0:48:14.80,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why we take the cheating parts so seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.46,0:48:14.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们认真对待作弊的那方面
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.82,0:48:20.89,English,,0,0,0,,Because if you do these labs you're going to learn an incredible amount of really cool stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.82,0:48:20.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为如果你认真做这些实验，你会学到一大堆非常酷的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.74,0:48:23.42,English,,0,0,0,,If you don't do them you won't learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.74,0:48:23.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你不这样做，你将不会学到任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.44,0:48:30.42,English,,0,0,0,,So each one of these labs is 1-2 weeks each
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.44,0:48:30.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以每个实验的长度都是 1-2 周
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.18,0:48:36.22,English,,0,0,0,,And involves typically some kind of programming or measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.18,0:48:36.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通常涉及某种编程或测量数据
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.86,0:48:39.68,English,,0,0,0,,There's also two exams a midterm and a final
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.86,0:48:39.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有两个考试是期中考试和期末考试
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.00,0:48:50.98,English,,0,0,0,,The exams are proctored they're online proctored in Wayne and and in Gates
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.00,0:48:50.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些考试被监督，他们是在线考试并且有监考，在 Wayne 和 Gates 教学楼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.40,0:48:55.10,English,,0,0,0,,What we do for the exams is we have like we take like four days
