Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.08,0:49:01.02,English,,0,0,0,,And then we have like multiple clusters that are Network isolated
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.08,0:49:01.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们有像网络隔离的多个组
