Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.48,0:49:20.52,English,,0,0,0,,So it's nominally like 80 minutes but we give you like a five or six hour window to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.48,0:49:20.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以虽然它名义上是 80 分钟，但我们给你五六个小时内的任意时间去做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.24,0:49:26.87,English,,0,0,0,,Okay so there's so you can sign up any time any day that there's a slot
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.24,0:49:26.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，所以你可以在任何时间任何时候注册考试时间
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.28,0:49:30.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay so there's flexibility so you can kind of tailor it to your schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.28,0:49:30.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，所以考试有灵活性，你可以按照你的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.38,0:49:34.96,English,,0,0,0,,And we I think we've also removed all the time pressure right so which is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.38,0:49:34.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且我们认为我们也将所有的时间压力都排除在外，所以
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.70,0:49:39.98,English,,0,0,0,,You can go back you can check your work you can just kind of relax
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.70,0:49:39.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以回去看看你的答案，你可以放松一下
