Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.26,0:51:14.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个机会非常高，你会很快收到回复
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.88,0:51:20.50,English,,0,0,0,,The the disadvantage of having this advantage of this mailing list is that it allows us to control the message
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.88,0:51:20.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使用邮箱的优点是它允许我们控制消息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.78,0:51:26.36,English,,0,0,0,,And control what we're it's what feedback we' re giving back to you
